{"tid":1790252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民記問卷調查結果公佈］黑警凍結香港人嘅錢 而自己想加人工？","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T05:53:06.000Z","uid":325953,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e0da704f3bb323285b8e2703f3eaaaf860f1194b","tid":1790252,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">超過98.6%受訪者反對警察加薪，佢哋話因為....</div></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HNazpfX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHNazpfX.jpg&h=90bc7fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第七次民記問卷調查結果發佈</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26GSaYO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26GSaYO.jpg&h=0d54ab4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWu8tLv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWu8tLv.jpg&h=1838be41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cWyESc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cWyESc.jpg&h=0c9b4bab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBcxVqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBcxVqz.jpg&h=22c9b19c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXy1OLB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXy1OLB.jpg&h=9a23bc21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNzkjSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNzkjSi.jpg&h=078cb0f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba424e89bec6d78b81ddbd4f9ab6ade721d1b466","tid":1790252,"uid":325953,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:11:51.000Z","msg":"警隊加薪問卷調查結果<br />\n想凍結香港人錢 仲要加黑警人工？<br />\n.<br />\n民間記者會就近日有關提高公務員包括警隊薪金的議案發起問卷調查，結果顯示近99%受訪反對警察加薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，92.4%受訪者認同警察和其他公務員的加薪議案應分開審議。多月來警察瀆職、濫暴濫捕，近九成半受訪者對警方評分繼續給予零分。民調結果各項數據均充分顯示警察並無加薪之理。<br />\n.<br />\n政府和保皇黨必須重新考慮加薪方案，分開審議警隊和其他公務員薪酬，並凍結或減少警員薪酬和津貼，停止將警隊提升為社會的特權階級，聆聽已經非常清晰的民意。<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問卷調查結果新聞稿：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36U8G1B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36U8G1B&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5XvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=187f2f7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36U8G1B</a>"},{"pid":"dfee12c2678eaede639ea1776c7db070c08e4039","tid":1790252,"uid":325953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"Survey Results on Pay Raise for Police Forex<br />\n<br />\nThe Citizens&rsquo; Press Conference conducted a survey on public opinion towards the recently proposed resolution to raise pay for the civil services, including the Hong Kong Police Force. Results show that nearly 99% of respondents oppose a pay raise for police <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, and that 92.4% agree that pay raise should be separately considered for police and for the rest of the civil services. With month after month of police misconduct and brutality, nearly 95% of respondents gave a satisfaction rating of zero out of ten for the police. Summing up results, all statistics from our public poll clearly indicate that the proposal to raise pay for the police is completely unreasonable.<br />\n<br />\nThe resolution to raise pay for the police seems to be all but another stunt by Beijing&rsquo;s henchmen to appease their master, and should and must reconsidered and withdrawn. The proposition of a pay raise for the Police Force and other civil services must be separated; salaries and benefits for the police force should also be frozen and/or reduced accordingly. <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />English press release:<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2McmBIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2McmBIE&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5XvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=1c03f31c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2McmBIE</a>"},{"pid":"bbc5c804bd3844ec59502885f8c7e9641d79709b","tid":1790252,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e285f16bb7da012183455d8885a4be94a03c04","tid":1790252,"uid":58160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加你老母啦"},{"pid":"202b70931d2ef9941a60931b907f3c17e7ef6fc6","tid":1790252,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcec5d5dcf2a31aa423c9caa0017986300efe11","tid":1790252,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c666fa646a4e2ff444b48a3e2a5ea0758ec1fc8","tid":1790252,"uid":58160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\